reviewText: Some what entertaining, but not very educational.  The audio was terrible; I could barely hear most of the segments.  Sending it back
I really enjoyed this CD.  It was very informative and the gardens were beautiful.  Worth watching.  Definitely recommend this CD to others!!!!!

This is a really good dvd about gardening. It has good information on garden makeovers.and it gives good ides about designs. If you are a do-it-your type of person this dvd will be really helpful to you.
